target: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_00<tab>ショートストップ野営地のタップクリクスは、冒険者を疑いの目で見ている。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_01<tab>Tapklix accuses you of being a thief sent by the Illuminati. Uninterested in your words, he insists that you let your actions attest to your innocence by finding and eliminating an Illuminati patrol.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_01<tab>タップクリクスから、廃品を奪っていく「青の手」とは無関係だと証明するよう求められた。低地ドラヴァニアのシャーレアン工匠街で「青の手」を討伐しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_02<tab>You stop the patrol in its tracks and leave no survivors. However, you sense there are yet more Illuminati lurking nearby. Find them and eliminate them.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_02<tab>「青の手」を討伐した。まだ廃品を奪おうとしている「青の手」がいるようだ。シャーレアン工匠街で再度「青の手」を討伐しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_03<tab>The last of the Illuminati have been dealt with. Return to Tapklix now that your allegiance is clear.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_03<tab>「青の手」を再度討伐した。ショートストップ野営地の「タップクリクス」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_04<tab>Tapklix is glad to have seen your battle against the Illuminati. Using the age-old logic that the enemy of his enemy is his friend, he concludes that you are a true friend to the goblins of Idyllshire.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_SEQ_04<tab>タップクリクスに報告した。彼は「青の手」を倒した冒険者を仲間と認めてくれた。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TODO_00<tab>Slay Illuminati patrols at the designated area.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TODO_00<tab>シャーレアン工匠街で「青の手」を討伐

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TODO_01<tab>Slay Illuminati at the other designated area.

TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_000Pshhh... Shkohhh...
You are stranger! You are sneakypeeker! You are thief working for Illuminati!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_000シュコォ……シュコォ……
最近「青の手」　ここらの廃品　奪ってく！
ゴブたち集めた　ここらの廃品　奪ってく！

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_001<tab>You can't take these things! No, no, no! They are for all to enjoy! But Illuminati always try to steal and hide things. Tapklix must be on constant guard.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_001ところであにた　「青の手」連中　無関係？
ゴブは　あにたが仲間と　信じたい～。
でもでも　これも　お仕事だ～　警戒　するの　お仕事だ～。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_002<tab>If you say you are gobbiefriend, then prove it! Find Illuminati and defeat them. Drive them away from this place!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_002無関係だと　言うのなら　証明　証明　大証明！
「青の手」見つけて　迎撃し　ゴブらの仲間と　証明せよ！

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_010<tab>Prove you are gobbiefriend! Find Illuminati and defeat them!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_010無関係だと　言うのなら　証明　証明　大証明！
「青の手」見つけて　迎撃し　ゴブらの仲間と　証明せよ！

TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_BALLOON_000_105シュコォ…シュコォ…
ズタズタだ～！

TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_BALLOON_000_110シュコォ…シュコォ…
バラバラだ～！

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_020<tab>Prove you are gobbiefriend! Find Illuminati and defeat them!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_020無関係だと　言うのなら　証明　証明　大証明！
「青の手」見つけて　迎撃し　ゴブらの仲間と　証明せよ！
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_BALLOON_000_115<tab>仲間　倒れた　やり返せ～！

TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_BALLOON_000_120シュコォ…シュコォ…
切りきざめ～！

TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_BALLOON_000_125シュコォ…シュコォ…
ぶった切れ～！

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_030Pshhh... Shkohhh...
You slew Illuminati fightyforce! You are true gobbiefriend.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_030シュコォ……シュコォ……
「青の手」倒した　冒険者　ゴブははなから　信じてた～！
さっすが　ゴブの目　狂いなし～！

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_031<tab>The things here are for all people of Idyllshire. But Illuminati try to steal them away!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_031ここらの廃品　ゴブらのもの！
手出しするヤツ　容赦なし～！

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_032<tab>Illuminati is our enemy. Illuminati is your enemy. This means you are our friend!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ806_01936_TAPKLIX_000_032「青の手」連中　ゴブらの敵！
「青の手」連中　あにたの敵！
つまり　ゴブらは　お仲間ね～！！
